Class ProductVariant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shopify.buy.model.ShopifyObject
      • com.shopify.buy.model.ProductVariant

  • public class ProductVariant
extends ShopifyObject
    Represents a specific version of Product. Each variant has a different combination of size, color or other option(s).
